#Subtitle2
幫我把下面的英文字幕，保留原來的英文，加上 "--" 符號，再加上中文翻譯

1
00:01,906 --> 00:04,296
You were born here. Raised here.
 -- 你在這裡出生，長大。

2
00:05,148 --> 00:07,257
This dome is the only world you've ever known.
 -- 這個圓頂是你所認識的唯一世界。

3
00:09,531 --> 00:13,117
There's a place just off past the eastern ridge. Right there.
 -- 在東邊山脈的遠處有個地方，就在那裡。

4
00:13,488 --> 00:15,437
Dad, what are you talking about?
 -- 爸，你在說什麼？

5
00:15,617 --> 00:16,343
You'll see.
 -- 你會明白的。

6
00:17,326 --> 00:18,427
Get out there.
 -- 去那裡。

7
00:21,553 --> 00:22,591
To the crater.
 -- 去那個隕石坑。

8
00:24,21 --> 00:25,122
Whatever's out there,
 -- 無論有什麼，

9
00:25,173 --> 00:26,146
your dad wants you to see it.
 -- 你爸爸希望你去看看。

10
00:26,197 --> 00:28,60
We've never even been outside the dome before.
 -- 我們從未去過圓頂之外。

12
00:28,968 --> 00:29,865
So what's it going to be?
 -- 你們決定怎麼做？

13
00:29,916 --> 00:30,904
We're leaving tonight.
 -- 我們今晚就出發。

14
00:30,955 --> 00:32,192
I hear she's weird.
 -- 我聽說她很奇怪。

15
00:32,244 --> 00:32,857
Why?
 -- 為什麼？

16
00:32,908 --> 00:33,771
She's from Earth.
 -- 她來自地球。

17
00:33,822 --> 00:35,185
So? They're peculiar.
 -- 那又怎樣？他們很奇特。

18
00:35,243 --> 00:36,231
You're peculiar.
 -- 你也很奇特。

19
00:36,308 --> 00:37,75
All in favor？
 -- 大家都贊成嗎？

20
00:39,515 --> 00:40,708
Let's go steal a rover.
 -- 讓我們去偷一輛月球車。

21
00:43,255 --> 00:44,849
The lockdown will commence...
 -- 封鎖措施即將啟動...

22
00:44,900 --> 00:45,638
Come on.
 -- 快點。

23
00:45,689 --> 00:46,669
...in five...
 -- ...五...

24
00:47,21 --> 00:47,739
...four...
 -- ...四...

25
00:48,256 --> 00:48,974
...three...
 -- ...三...

26
00:49,326 --> 00:50,44
...two...
 -- ...二...

27
00:50,552 --> 00:51,199
...one.
 -- ...一。

28
00:56,555 --> 00:58,250
You know the best thing about road trips?
 -- 你知道公路旅行最好的事情嗎？

29
00:59,993 --> 01:01,828
You get to leave everything behind.
 -- 你可以把一切都拋在腦後。

30
01:06,134 --> 01:07,294
Here it is,
 -- 到了，

31
01:07,345 --> 01:09,599
bottom of the ninth... the wind up.
 -- 九局末... 準備投球。

32
01:20,980 --> 01:23,550
The sky on Earth. Is it really blue?
 -- 地球上的天空，真的是藍色的嗎？

33
01:23,601 --> 01:24,315
Yeah.
 -- 是的。

34
01:24,366 --> 01:25,260
Wow.
 -- 哇。

35
01:25,770 --> 01:27,456
The most important thing to remember...
 -- 最重要的是要記住...

36
01:27,618 --> 01:29,175
This is a bad idea.
 -- 這是個糟糕的主意。

37
01:31,340 --> 01:33,544
Watch out! Watch out!
 -- 小心！小心！

38
01:33,724 --> 01:35,854
It's not just about where you're going.
 -- 重點不只在於目的地

40
01:38,53 --> 01:39,91
Meteor shower!
 -- 流星雨！

41
01:39,782 --> 01:41,380
Addison! Run!
 -- Addison！快跑！

42
01:42,282 --> 01:43,895
It's about how you get there.
 -- 重要的是前往的過程

43
01:45,513 --> 01:46,872
The people you get there with.
 -- 和同行的夥伴

44
01:47,622 --> 01:49,240
Caleb, what's in the crater?
 -- Caleb，坑洞裡有什麼？

45
01:49,519 --> 01:50,245
I don't know.
 -- 我不知道

46
01:51,351 --> 01:52,466
Guess we'll find out.
 -- 猜猜看，我們會發現什麼

47
01:52,517 --> 01:54,222
You guys go first.
 -- 你們先去

48
01:55,17 --> 01:57,398
You're never quite the same as you were when you began.
 -- 完成旅程後，你會不同於出發時的自己

50
01:57,516 --> 02:10,359
These were the best two days of my life.
 -- 這是我一生中最美好的兩天


